[[=image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment%3Ait-always-ends-the-same-7/cell.jpg]]
You hit send. 

You're happy with the composition. You didn't stress over the wording, didn't debate the use of emojis. It felt natural. //This// feels natural. 

A day goes by. No response. They must be busy.

But then another.

And another.

Soon it's the night before you asked to meet. You break your rule, you text again.

Thursday comes. Still no response.

= It always ends the same.

= //[[[https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/it-always-ends-the-same/offset/9 |Continue?]]]//
